node.text: @foycelexuan wine makes one optimistic 😀 and look forward to better days ahead 🍷🍷🌹🌹🌹

My single video has hit 1 MILLION views. Today at 1,083,035 views 🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉🎉🎉🏆
. My good friend has always encourged me, don't worry, the people that likes u is always more than the people that hate u. Well, i don't think so. 🤔  I believe they r equal. 😂 I has equal number of Fans & Haters. 50%-50%. Therefore, I will like to take this moment to specially address to my haters. HATERS, thanks for your contribution of this half a million from yr side, without u i will nv make it happen. & if u wish to further contribute, u can kindly click on the video link & rewatch it here. 😉 https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157952684953260&id=676608259
.
. #quotestoliveby whoever is trying to bring u down, is already below u . ❌Haters, while u thought that u r pulling me down, u're actually pushing me ABOVE. .
.For my Fans💗. I saw the constant requests. Sorry, I did not post out any video for whole of this month, despite during this circuit breaker many others hv go on Live stream or make tik-tok videos. No video here is NOT because i don't hv lottery. I could hv be in my usual sexy doing video on cooking, singing, wierd dancing or even jus bitching. But i chose this breaker time to slightly detox away to spend time with little animals instead of facing Humans. You can nv finish chasing FAME. Fame 是追不完的。🔥Fame is a thing, that u will realise when u stop chasing, it will still come chasing after yr backside.🍑 It is when serenity is scarce, especially in this time of pandemic, a calm spirit gives u peace amid the storm. Nevertheless, to thk u fans for yr long support & standing up for me, i will still make a video soon since its the celebration of 1million! Lastly sincerely thank you.
